<div class="title">Nice and Happy</div>
<div class="substance">Nimetazepam</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Lee&Exact=1">Lee</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Lee. "Nice and Happy: An Experience with Nimetazepam (exp84713)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Apr 12, 2016. erowid.org/exp/84713</div>

